{
  "stem": "14002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They all assembled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had all to assemble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My-- my aunt and uncle in Teresva with eight children, they had to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in other words, they took them away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't know where they're going to take them or for what.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took them away to Galicia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We never heard from them again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's why I wonder, why I cannot hear or-- or read anything about it, what happened to those thousands of Jews from-- from the Carpathian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That they took them away in 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I know one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They took them to the Kamenets-Podolsk, in Galicia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- and I would say, 98% of them never made it alive from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At that time I realized-- I started to realize what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But my father, he was in Germany when Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He always told us what he saw, what they did in Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So he was more afraid than we.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We didn't realize it yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We didn't realize what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't take any Jews to the military.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But they took in the-- the Hungarians, that is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They took in whoever was military-- military age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They took them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They called it munkatabor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That means, in Hungarian, work camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they used to do, let's say, when the war started with Russia, they used to take those people, they used to get them on the Russian front, well, to dig trenches and so on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Most of them never came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So I-- I've seen, already, what's-- what's going on there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I went to Budapest, well, to look for some work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "My sister, Chia, the older sister, she went to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She found some work there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
